{"type": "article", "id": 43865, "title": "艾格巴黎退市，以及，Lush 推出助眠润肤乳 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-08-08T03:30:08Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1231, "name": "PUMA"}, {"id": 10620, "name": "乒乓球"}, {"id": 18579, "name": "OFF-WHITE"}, {"id": 19483, "name": "lush"}, {"id": 20739, "name": "STUSSY"}, {"id": 2273, "name": "乐天"}, {"id": 22831, "name": "Etam"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170808102459S61cx2tFVmvOWpMs.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/etam-delist-french-stock-market-10957855/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>法国服装品牌 Etam 要退市</strong></a> | 创办于 1916 年，于 1997 年登陆巴黎证券交易所上市的法国服装品牌 Etam 宣布，将在周三正式从巴黎证券交易所退市，目前股票交易已暂停。Etam 表示，集团将会把发展重点从成衣部门转向内衣部门，重点关注墨西哥、智利与韩国等新兴市场的业务。</p><p><a href=\"https://www.financemagnates.com/institutional-forex/technology/rakuten-reports-positive-financial-results-h1-2017/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>日本乐天发布半年财报，利润大涨近 50% </strong></a>| 截止至 6 月 30 日的上半年，日本电商平台乐天的利润大涨了 49.2%，至 3.63 亿美元，销售额同比上涨了 19.3%，至 39.7 亿美元。该集团目前主要业务仍然是日本地区的电商业务，未来将进一步向全球其它地区扩张。</p><p><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIzMjc1OTg5NA==&amp;mid=2247487153&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=d4cff4c13d5417b695438b3460eb5438&amp;chksm=e88eb988dff9309ecc5840ebcfc631c904e11394c2ed9c3c044ac2c17bacb7eee78d617aa302&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=0808gzEv6DTYAHehsRd8ZW8A#rd\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>《纽约时报》将推出第一本独立发行的中文旅行杂志 </strong></a>| 栩栩华生媒体集团和《纽约时报》合作，将在 8 月 10 日正式推出中文旅行杂志《NYT Travel 新视线》创刊号。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>日本品牌<a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/456313\" rel=\"nofollow\"> MAISON MIHARA YASUHIRO 2018 早春系列</a>发布，lookbook 拍得很美。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170808102540vYOSEX7aoF1CMpRP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.507538\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170808102539npoYf9EUzJvmhrgq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.507538\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170808102541JEWkjRv2MbOC7Tmg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.507538\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170808102541p17gRZJ6KPyxMD8a.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.507538\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170808102543tqBJH8GMhRgmIdoW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.507538\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170808102542w2zygdmAkQ6VY1aP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.507538\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170808102548sn7PEwgqTQDAx3tf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.507538\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708081025492wxWiQXhDlpnBEmM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.507538\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170808102549Cpx7SVK0XZohkEPG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.507538\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170808102539EAxot67Z3VpMHrcG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.663333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170808102541lBjgeM9IkHVd1N4D.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.663333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170808102543MwZufTnL1maPW5ls.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.663333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170808102548Gf9mok5r4yvxQdMl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.663333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708081025482vWcyhVCieSmfZRX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.663333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170808102550qZTR0du1PN3U9EDb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.663333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/8/off-white-70s-sneaker-high-red-white\" rel=\"nofollow\">Off-White 全新的 70s Sneaker High 鞋款</a>正式上架。这双鞋号称是在意大利纯手工制作，白色高筒皮革鞋身搭配鞋头处的棕色麂皮，以红色交叉箭头 logo 点缀，另外配上了易于穿脱的拉链，定价为 647 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708081027328sZ4R0GnBQ5NEWFu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708081027320n7fRcmygrFYG16P.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708081027364dC1tHhiERMcUX0A.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>Kate Spade 在 1999 年推出的独立男性品牌 <a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/8/jack-spade-ping-pong-paddle-case\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jack Spade 推出了一款帆布制乒乓球袋</a>。另外附赠两副球拍和一个球，售价为 98 美元。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170808102833mZHeto8yplRduXOF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708081028338Iwlsr37cmC6uNao.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708081028384TIpfYRLJZxKOWAU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>盆栽哥与 PUMA 合作的鞋款<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/8/the-weeknd-puma-parallel-sneaker\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Parallel 正式发售</a>。这是 The Weeknd 担任 PUMA 全球品牌大使的首款签名球鞋，定价为 220 美元，将于 8 月 24 日起在 KITH、The Webster 及 Barneys 等指定店铺发售，此外还有 T-Shirt、丹宁外套与裤款等单品也将一起推出。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170808102913GhCMdIXPzn02g7iu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665812\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170808102913w4k8dahVNlRcz6OE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665812\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170808102908dY4pBDTX7CiOygbo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665812\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170808102908zlX8Z9ujVfm6sHAo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170808102908AHi2ORk1uSQfLEcp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665812\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170808102917ws1EhLnvxeNpzgQD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666963\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>针对失眠患者，Lush 推出了一款名为 <a href=\"http://popbee.com/beauty/skincare/lush-sleepy-body-lotion-helps-with-insomnia/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sleepy </a>的润肤乳。据说这款乳液用上了薰衣草和香豆这两种芳香疗法，睡前涂上可以帮助入眠，消除焦虑。不知道有没有效果，不过售价只有 10 美元。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170808102941tRZI3GEUgrjaXecb.png\" data-ratio=\"0.998476\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/8/stussy-2017-fall-winter-lookbook\" rel=\"nofollow\">Stüssy 正式发布 2017 秋冬系列</a>。该系列包括大量外套，结合了迷彩、斑马纹、印花等图案，将于 8 月 11 日陆续发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170808103004An4a6oDKQMsTz8fH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498638\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170808103000oi81OPTcMR0EGAku.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170808103000sIP8YC9mL4tAkZ3T.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170808103000A0ZoJeg9S8bqHEOD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498547\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170808103002nS05ksxqupgvj3Rl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708081030013UZtoSshuVkpPQl7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170808103002lA3SCeh9tiI6VFzE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170808103001bw5PDGMnLpHQCI97.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170808103002WpIu1qi7LENracyz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170808103001e8rEzFDCtIvlBgJp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：<a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/456313\" rel=\"nofollow\">wwd</a></p>"}